{"title":"Cane Creek Chroma Studio lets you Color Match Headsets, BBs, Forks & More","link":"https://bikerumor.com/cane-creek-chroma-studio-lets-you-color-match-headsets-bbs-forks-more/","date":1698011457000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-headsets.jpg\" alt=\"Cane Creek Chroma Studio color-matched anodizing for headsets\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-headsets.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-headsets-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-headsets-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-headsets-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-headsets-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-headsets-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-headsets-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Cane Creek’s new Chroma Studio collection lets you add a hit of Blue, Red, Gold or Silver to your bike, or color match it all the way through. Available for their most popular components and some finishing bits, here’s what’s on offer:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Hellbender 70 Headsets</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Headset topcaps</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hellbender 70 Bottom Brackets</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Crank Preloaders</li>\n\n\n\n<li>eeBarkeeps (road &amp; MTB)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Helm MKII adjustment knobs, caps, and decals</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-helm-fork-adjustment-knobs.jpg\"><img width=\"1202\" height=\"999\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-helm-fork-adjustment-knobs.jpg\" alt=\"Cane Creek Chroma Studio color-matched anodizing for HELM fork knobs and dials and decals\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-helm-fork-adjustment-knobs.jpg 1202w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-helm-fork-adjustment-knobs-297x247.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-helm-fork-adjustment-knobs-800x665.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-helm-fork-adjustment-knobs-120x100.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-helm-fork-adjustment-knobs-768x638.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The colors will be available for all four complete current Hellbender 70 headset variations, and the Hellbender 70 Bottom Brackets are available in threaded BSA options to fit 30mm, 29mm, an 24mm spindles. BB’s include color-matched bearing covers, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-cockpit-parts.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1201\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-cockpit-parts.jpg\" alt=\"Cane Creek Chroma Studio color-matched anodizing for headsets, fork knobs, bottom brackets and small parts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-cockpit-parts.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-cockpit-parts-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-cockpit-parts-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-cockpit-parts-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-cockpit-parts-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-cockpit-parts-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-cockpit-parts-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-BB-crank-lockring.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1201\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-BB-crank-lockring.jpg\" alt=\"Cane Creek Chroma Studio color-matched anodizing for bottom brackets and crank adjustment rings\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-BB-crank-lockring.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-BB-crank-lockring-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-BB-crank-lockring-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-BB-crank-lockring-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-BB-crank-lockring-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-BB-crank-lockring-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/canecreek-chroma-studio-anodized-BB-crank-lockring-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out the full collection on their website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://canecreek.com/chroma-studio/\" target=\"_blank\">CaneCreek.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/cane-creek-chroma-studio-lets-you-color-match-headsets-bbs-forks-more/\">Cane Creek Chroma Studio lets you Color Match Headsets, BBs, Forks &amp; More</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb8370068